creator: Computer Services Inc.
descriptionHtml:
With HIGH PLAINS BANK’S Mobile Banking App you can safely and securely access your accounts anytime, anywhere. Our mobile app is FREE and allows you to:

• View your balance
• View account activity
• Transfer funds
• Locate a branch or ATM
• Contact our Customer Service
• Share our app with friends and family



Security
Security is our priority. Rest assured that your personal information is kept safe!

Contact Us
You can contact us at 1-580-546-7511 if you have any questions about the High Plains Bank Mobile App or the self-service registration process.
